Methods theory : 

method is a block of code which is used to perform a task or operation

method syntax:

  //method head or method signature
   access_specifier access_modifier return_type method_name(args/no args)
   {
   //method implementation or method body
   }
  
 Types of methods -- 4 types
 1.Method without arguments and without return type
 2.Method without arguments  and with return type
 3.Method with arguments and with return type
 4.Method with argument and without return type

 
 